description:
This week on Unqualified, Anna and Sim sit down with comedy veteran Bob Odenkirk (Better Call Saul, Breaking Bad, Mr. Show)! They chat about making the switch to dramatic acting, dog strollers, armpit hair and so much more! Bob also runs into Kayla in the lobby of a hotel and has a high profile general meeting with Karen Sarducci. They then call Sophia, who doesn’t know what to do when her boyfriend’s best friend is blatantly rude to her and Jamie, whose boyfriend becomes territorial about her past relationships!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
